Package org.apache.fulcrum.pool

Interface InitableRecyclable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Recyclable
    public interface InitableRecyclable
extends Recyclable
    An interface for objects that can be pooled and recycled several times by different clients. Pooled objects that implement this interface use no argument or recycle methods. Initialization is taken care of using the init method. This is a way to avoid introspection/reflection when pooling an object.
